posting_body: ['The Lighthouse', '10710 SE 256th Street, Kent, WA, 98030', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 23', 'OR Text', '23', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team.', 'Visit This Website to See More:', '<URL>', 'Welcome to The Lighthouse Apartment Homes!', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 970 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Perfectly placed in Kent, Washington, the Lighthouse Apartments is located only minutes away from Kent Station and the infamous ShoWare Center where there is endless shopping and entertainment options.', 'The Lighthouse Apartments offers one, two and three bedroom apartments and is a pet friendly community, allowing both cats and dogs with only a few breed restrictions.', 'With graceful style, The Lighthouse Apartment Homes exemplify unique details and thoughtful touches rarely found in an apartment community.', '*Deposits & Fees:', 'Refundable security deposit: $400.00 (on approved credit)', 'Non-refundable administrative fee: $250.00', 'Application fee (per applicant 18+): $44.00', 'Pet Policy', 'The Lighthouse Apartment Homes welcomes your furry loved ones with some weight and breed restrictions.', 'Please contact the management office for more information.', 'Pet Rent & Fees:', 'Cats: $25.00/month', 'Dogs: $35.00/month', 'Refundable Pet Deposit: $250.00 per pet', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'ShoWare Center Kent Station Great Wall Shopping Mall Soos Creek Trailhead Riverbend Golf Complex Apartments for Rent in Kent Luxury Apartments Affordable Apartments Renovated Apartments Upgraded Washer and dryer Pet Friendly Kent Auburn Kent Meridian High School Meridian Middle School East Hill Elementary School Pioneer Elementary School', 'Olympic Middle School Gildo Rey Elementary School Boeing', 'DCh1hMC74']
